### SUMMARY

This is a comprehensive Spring Boot 3 + PostgreSQL RICMS system with:
- **Security:** Fine-grained RBAC (ROLE_/PERM_ authorities), AES-256-GCM encryption for sensitive fields, JWT authentication
- **Idempotency:** Time-windowed (10-minute) idempotency on orders via hashed keys and row-level timestamps
- **Work Orders:** Full lifecycle with pessimistic locking (double-claim guard), cost locking on resolution, SLA tracking, ratings
- **Exports:** CSV/XLSX export from AdminController and WorkOrderController with permission enforcement
- **Testing:** 8 unit test classes + 8 API test shell scripts covering all major features

